grep -i Port /etc/ssh/ssh_config  #case insensitive
grep Port *  #all files
grep -r Port * #recursive ~
grep -ri Error /var/log
alias grep='grep --color=auto'
| `grep -w "term" file`    | Match whole word only                                |
| `grep -r "term" folder`  | Recursively search in all files in folder            |
| `grep -o "term" file`    | Print only the matching part of the line             |
| `grep -c "term" file`    | Count the number of matching lines                   |
| `grep -inw "term" file`  | Combine case-insensitive, line numbers, and whole word|
